/a>\r\n<script>!function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],p=/^http:/.test(d.location)?\'http\':\'https\';if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src=p+\"://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\";fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document,\"script\",\"twitter-wjs\");</script>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Sponsors\";s:4:\"text\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:4;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:28:\"New at Killer Diller Weekend\";s:4:\"text\";s:1365:\"<i>Why Killer Diller Weekend 2014 is the year to come!</i>\r\n<br /><br />\r\nThis year we kick off a new type of event. Killer Diller Weekend has officially become the annual showcase for Savoy Swing Club. We will be showcasing performances from all around Seattle, and more than that we hope to showcase our new education program as well. Savoy Swing Club has been working diligently to improve it\'s mission through Seattle, and has finally landed on its path. We need your help to support our mission, which is why now part of Killer Diller Weekend is a fundraiser to support education of Swing Dancing in Seattle\'s schools.\r\n<br /><br/ >\r\nIf that doesn\'t convince you yet, we are looking for top sponsors to help us run this event to ensure the maximum amount of proceeds go to support this venture. Working with local foundations, we aim to bring you the best representation of Swing Dancing to Seattle: Take a look at what we are offering this year: \r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Live Music Overnight</li>\r\n  <li>Late Night Adult Cabaret</li>\r\n  <li>Fundraiser with all ages performances</li>\r\n  <li>Catered Events</li>\r\n  <li>World Class Instructors throughout the day</li>\r\n  <li>Exciting Dances to live music</li>\r\n  <li>And more to come!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRegistration will be available starting September 1st, so grab the best prices before the cost goes up! See you this winter!\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:5;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"text\";s:243:\"<br />\r\n<p><a href=\"mailto: