r the disciplined student and skilled competitor, Laura began winning national titles and gaining recognition as a championship lindy hop follow with an independent style and point of view. She loves dancing with a wide variety of leads with diverse styles and ideas to challenge and broaden her own abilities as a follow. And as an instructor, she brings a fresh perspective towards developing each student’s technical foundation and individual style. For Laura, every dance is a chance to put smiles on peoples’ faces with an entertaining performance which shares and inspires the joy and excitement for swing dancing.','Laura Keat','','publish','closed','closed','','laura-keat','','','2014-08-17 04:30:43','2014-08-17 04:30:43','',0,'http://localhost:9000/?post_type=sc-speakers&#038;p=22',0,'sc-speakers','',0),(25,1,'2014-07-01 06:55:59','2014-07-01 06:55:59','Jeremy Otth amassed a great amount of knowledge on the historic essence of vintage swing dances from many of the original jitterbuggs and swing dancers. Along with his seemingly inexhaustible amount of energy, Jeremy’s natural talent and dedication led him to accumulate championship titles at many acclaimed dance competitions such as the International Lindy Hop Championships, National Jitterbug Championships, American Classic Balboa Championships and the US Open Swing Dance Championships. Jeremy is now able to share that breadth of knowledge and passion for these classic partner dances by entertaining and educating feet from Southern California to around the world.','Jeremy Otth','','publish','closed','closed','','jeremy-otth','','','2014-08-17 04:30:25','2014-08-17 04:30:25','',0,'http://localhost:9000/?post_type=sc-speakers&#038;p=25',0,'sc-speakers','',0),(27,1,'2014-07-01 07:19:35','2014-07-01 07:19:35','','Auto Draft','','trash','closed','closed','','auto-draft','','','2014-08-17 04:24:44','2014-08-17 04:24:44','',0,'http://localhost:9000/?post_type=sc-rotator&#038;p=27',0,'sc-rotator','',0),(29,1,'2014-07-01 0