9\">What is Killer Diller Weekend?</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h4>ANSWERS</h4>\r\n<h3 id=\"answer1\">1. What is included in the full weekend pass?</h3>\r\nThe full weekend pass gets you in to ALL of the Killer Diller Weekend events:\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Friday, Saturday and Sunday evening dances</li>\r\n	<li>2 days of classes (not including Master’s classes)</li>\r\n	<li>Admission to Late Night Events</li>\r\n	<li>Admission to Friday Late Night Cabaret</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"answer2\">2. What is included in the Dance &amp; Show pass?</h3>\r\nThe Dance &amp; Show pass gets you into the Friday, Saturday and Sunday evening dances, the Vintage Fashion Gala, and the Killer Diller Cabaret.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"answer3\">3. Can I sign up for individual classes?</h3>\r\nOnly if space permits. You pay at the door, and the availability is on a first-come, first-served basis. The cost is $20 per class. If you wish to drop in on Advanced level classes, you must attend the track audition on Saturday morning, or have express permission from the organizers.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"answer4\">4. It looks like there are 2 masters classes this year, is that right? How will that work??</h3>\r\nYes! There will be 2 masters classes this year! Each masters class costs $25, or $40 for both.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"answer5\">5. How do I sign up for Master’s classes?</h3>\r\nMaster’s classes are by invitation only. Registration is online and there is limited space in these classes. Contact kdw@savoyswing.org if you would like to be considered for Master’s. The Master’s classes are for very experienced/master dancers – if you did not receive an invitation, you will be asked to provide names of instructors who can vouch for your level.The Master’s classes will not be held at the same time as 2 of the regular weekend classes. If you buy a full weekend pass and are invited to attend the Master’s classes, you will still need to pay for the Master’s classes. They will not be included in the full price of the weekend.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"answer6\">6. How do I sign up for Master’s classes?</h3>\r\nNo! Students will be encouraged to rotate partners in all classes.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"answer7\">7. I’m a beginner, can I take classes?</h3>\r\nThe workshops are designed for students who are comfortable with the basics of Lindy Hop and have taken a few classes or workshops. For absolute beginner classes in the Seattle area, check out www.savoyswing.org.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"answer8\">8. Do I get into the fundraiser for free?</h3>\r\nWe are hoping to start a tradition with Killer Diller Weekend to hold a fundraiser for Savoy Swing Club\'s education programs. In addition to Killer Diller Weekend proceeds going to the education program, this event is the annual fundraiser for donors and supporters of this program. We encourage you to go, but the cost is separate from the full weekend pass and can be purchased at the door or by registration.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"answer9\">9. What is Killer Diller Weekend?</h3>\r\nKiller Diller Weekend is a community event to promote and showcase swing performance throughout Seattle. You will find live music, dance performances and amazing social dancing. We are excited to be part of Savoy Swing Club and it\'s ventures for education throughout the Pacific Northwest.','FAQ','','publish','open','open','','faq','','','2014-08-17 06:47:25','2014-08-17 06:47:25','',0,'http://localhost:9000/?page_id=44',0,'page','',0),(45,1,'2014-07-01 07:36:01','2014-07-01 07:36:01','','FAQ','','inherit','open','open','','44-revision-v1','','','2014-07-01 07:36:01','2014-07-01 07:36:01','',44,'http://localhost:9000/?p=45',0,'revision','',0),(46,1,'2014-07-01 07:37:07','2014-07-01 07:37:07','<div class=\"speaker\">\r\n<div class=\"one-half first\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"one-half\">\r\n<h2>Late Night Cabaret</h2>\r\nJoin us for an evening of shows and dances. We will be showcasing blues, burlesque and slow lindy performances. This is a suggested 21 and over event, and will be held concurrently with another of Savoy Swing Club\'s events: Blues Underground. More information to come...\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"speaker\">\r\n<div class=\"one-half first\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"one-half\">\r\n<h2>Saturday Fundraiser</h2>\r\nHave you heard what Savoy Swing Club is up to? We have some pretty large goals to fulfill our new mission, and we need your help. Join us to support education of swing dance throughout Seattle, and enjoy our live music, inspiration talks and performances throughout the night. Open Buffet and bar open before the events, so come early! More information to come...\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Special Events','','publish','open','open','','special-events','','','2014-08-17 07:09:10','2014-08-17 07:09:10','',0,'http://localhost:9000/?page_id=46',0,'page','',0),(47,1,'2014-07-01 07:37:07','2014-07-01 07:37:07','','Special Events','','inherit','open','open','','46-revision-v1','','','2014-07-01 07:37:07','2014-07-01 07:37:07','',46,'http://localhost:9000/?p=47',0,'revision','',0),(48,1,'2014-07-01 07:37:30','2014-07-01 07:37:30',' ','','','publish','open','open','','48','','','2014-08-17 04:37:41','2014-08-17 04:37:41','',0,'http://localhost:9000/?p=48',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(49,1,'2014-07-01 07:37:30','2014-07-01 07:37:30',' ','','','publish','open','open','','49','','','2014-08-17 04:37:41','2014-08-17 04:37:41','',0,'http://localhost:9000/?p=49',7,'nav_menu_item','',0),(50,1,'2014-07-01 07:57:26','2014-07-01 07:57:26','Sed vitae elit non lorem auctor lobortis. Nulla imperdiet accumsan feugiat. Ut lacinia nulla eget justo congue molestie. Donec congue metus in lorem lobortis consectetur. Nunc at dignissim tellus. Vivamus faucibus, elit eu vehicula porta, quam velit interdum eros, ctus sit amet eros.\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"53\" title=\"Main Contact\"]\r\n\r\n<h2>Hotels In the Area</h2>\r\n...','Con