&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;fb=1&amp;gl=us&amp;cid=8236118024542916974&amp;q=washington+hall+seattle&amp;ei=TzXwU9OsOoiJogSrz4LwBA&amp;ved=0CJoBEPwSMBM\">WASHINGTON HALL</a></h2>\r\nHistoric Seattle welcomes you to Washington Hall, a historic community gathering place. We invite you to explore this site to learn about facility rentals for events, the building’s history, the people who have contributed to its storied past and to its future, and our renovation project. Learn more about our anchor groups: 206 Zulu, Hidmo, and Voices Rising.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nWashington Hall’s mission is to create a transformative space in Seattle’s Central District that honors the history of Washington Hall and is a home for arts & culture that reflects its legacy.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"speaker\">\r\n<div class=\"one-half first\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/preview?client=safari&oe=UTF-8&ie=UTF-8&fb=1&gl=us&cid=15621407329568893016&q=Dance+Underground&ei=czzwU8nsBY_6oATC-4CwDw&ved=0CH8Q_BIwCQ\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-139\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Screen-Shot-2014-08-16-at-10.26.28-PM.png\" alt=\"Century Ballroom\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /></a>\r\n<h4><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/preview?client=safari&oe=UTF-8&ie=UTF-8&fb=1&gl=us&cid=15621407329568893016&q=Dance+Underground&ei=czzwU8nsBY_6oATC-4CwDw&ved=0CH8Q_BIwCQ\" target=\"_blank\">link to map</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"one-half\">\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/preview?client=safari&oe=UTF-8&ie=UTF-8&fb=1&gl=us&cid=15621407329568893016&q=Dance+Underground&ei=czzwU8nsBY_6oATC-4CwDw&ved=0CH8Q_BIwCQ\">Dance Underground</a></h2>\r\nEstablished in 2003, the Dance Underground is a Seattle based dance studio, co-owned and operated by two partners: Ilana Rubin and Tony Fan. Ilana and Tony are established dancers in Seattle with diverse dance backgrounds and teaching experiences.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nOur objective is to provide a warm, friendly atmosphere in an elegant setting that allows for optimum instruction and learning. We promote talented instructors who are recognized for their teaching excellence and their dedication to inspire their students to grow and express themselves creatively. We also promote friendly social dancing on weekend nights where people can have fun, get loose, and make new friends.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"speaker\">\r\n<div class=\"one-half first\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/preview?client=safari&amp;oe=UTF-8&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;fb=1&amp;gl=us&amp;cid=453526804850314761&amp;q=Century+Ballroom&amp;ei=GzXwU9y3HYv_oQSqo4DQBw&amp;ved=0CJEBEPwSMA0\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-139\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Screen-Shot-2014-08-16-at-9.48.24-PM.png\" alt=\"Century Ballroom\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /></a>\r\n<h4><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/preview?client=safari&amp;oe=UTF-8&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;fb=1&amp;gl=us&amp;cid=453526804850314761&amp;q=Century+Ballroom&amp;ei=GzXwU9y3HYv_oQSqo4DQBw&amp;ved=0CJEBEPwSMA0\">link to map</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"one-half\">\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/preview?client=safari&amp;oe=UTF-8&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;fb=1&amp;gl=us&amp;cid=453526804850314761&amp;q=Century+Ballroom&amp;ei=GzXwU9y3HYv_oQSqo4DQBw&amp;ved=0CJEBEPwSMA0\">CENTURY BALLROOM</a></h2>\r\nCentury Ballroom was founded in 1997 to promote social dancing of all kinds. Our community of instructors, staff and clients welcome and encourage any and everyone to come out dancing.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Venues','','publish','open','open','','venues','','','2014-08-17 05:27:34','2014-08-17 05:27:34','',0,'http://localhost:7001/?page_id=135',0,'page','',0),(136,1,'2014-08-17 04:37:28','2014-08-17 04:37:28','','Venues','','inherit','open','open','','135-revision-v1','','','2014-08-17 04:37:28','2014-08-17 04:37:28','',135,'http://localhost:7001/?p=136',0,'revision','',0),(137,1,'2014-08-17 04:37:41','2014-08-17 04:37:4